</div>
<div class="content-blue-bg">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="col-md-3 benefit-content">
      <h3>Community</h3>
      <p>We only focus on matching sklled trades and technical job seekers with employers.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 benefit-content">
